Package com.github.errantlinguist.io

Class Summary
ExtFilter A filename filter matching a given filename extension.
FileLineReader<L,F> A file reader class which reads in a data file or a directory of files, parses it/them, and returns an object representing the data therein.
FileParser<L,F> A Parser which parses a single line in a file of a given type.
ImmutableSetFileParser<O> A FileParser which creates an ImmutableSet from a file, with each item in the set corresponding to a single line in the file.
MapFileParser<O> A FileParser implementation which parses a file comprising two columns: A column of keys mapping to a second column of values.
RegexFileParser<L,F> A FileParser implementation which parses using regular expressions.
 

Exception Summary
FileParseException An Exception thrown if an error occurs during the parsing of a file.
